org.csc478.pokerGame.models

Class PokerScorer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.csc478.pokerGame.models.PokerScorer

  • public abstract class PokerScorer
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to score poker hands with sortable results.
    Implements Requirement:
    REQ061300 - Find best hand from 1-7 cards, REQ061301 - Royal Flush, REQ061302 - Straight Flush, REQ061303 - 4 of a Kind, REQ061304 - Full house, REQ061305 - Flush, REQ061306 - Straight, REQ061307 - 3 of a Kind, REQ061308 - 2 Pairs, REQ061309 - 1 Pair, REQ061310 - High Card
